## Pipeline Overview

The application exposes two main pipelines through the CLI menu:

### Ingestion Pipeline (Upload PDF / Video / Load Data)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Source[Source File\n(PDF / Video)]
    Extract[Extract Text\n(pypdf / Whisper + FFmpeg)]
    Chunk[Chunk Text\n(chunker.py)]
    Embed[Embed Chunks\n(embedder.py)]
    Store[Store in ChromaDB\n(vector_store.py)]

    Source --> Extract --> Chunk --> Embed --> Store
```

---

### Question-Answering Pipeline (Ask Question)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Question[User Question]
    Decide[Decide Action\n(action_resolver - LLM)]
    Retrieve[Retrieve Context\n(vector_store.py)]
    Generate[Generate Answer\n(question_resolver - LLM)]
    Reflect[Reflect on Answer\n(reflection_resolver - LLM)]

    Question --> Decide
    Decide -->|search| Retrieve --> Generate --> Reflect
    Decide -->|answer| Generate
```
